# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/

# Windows redirect artifact (self-respawns — see PROJECT.md Gotchas)
nul

# Session /export transcript dumps — full tool-call/reasoning logs. They stay
# LOCAL (repo is public): at root (careless /export) or inside a session's
# handoff folder. Curated HANDOFF.md/snapshots stay committed.
/2026-*.txt
docs/handoff/**/2026-*.txt
docs/handoff/**/transcript.md

# NOTE: .claude/ IS committed on purpose — agents, rules, commands and hooks are
# part of the prompt. Only the local-override files above are ignored.

# foglamp codebase-scan lock file holds an edit token — secret
.foglamp/
